Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.18,0:00:06.24,cloveropeng,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,200)}My hometown lay buried in snow the morning I was born.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.07,0:00:11.78,cloveropeng,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,200)}I looked up at the blue sky with my tiny hands.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.09,0:00:18.41,cloveropeng,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,200)}The face of the girl next door that I've known so well...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.14,0:00:23.27,cloveropeng,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,200)}It's as familiar as the graduation canon.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.27,0:00:29.23,cloveropeng,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,200)}Thriving in solitude has been mistaken as my life story.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.23,0:00:31.51,cloveropeng,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,200)}I want to blame it on someone.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.51,0:00:35.70,cloveropeng,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,200)}It's so difficult. No, I hate it.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.70,0:00:41.05,cloveropeng,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,200)}Tears and sorrow caused me to miss my chance.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.67,0:00:46.47,cloveropeng,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,200)}Autumn passed, winter came again, and I became a year older.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.10,0:00:53.26,cloveropeng,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,200)}You think you've run far away, but your story never ends.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.26,0:00:55.52,cloveropeng,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,200)}And yet, you're smirking.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.52,0:00:59.11,cloveropeng,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,200)}It's so cowardly. I hate it.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.11,0:01:05.25,cloveropeng,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,200)}Even if I have to cling to you, chase after you, and get kicked down...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.25,0:01:07.44,cloveropeng,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,200)}...I'll close the hole that's opened...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.44,0:01:10.36,cloveropeng,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,200)}...without a doubt. No...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.36,0:01:17.74,cloveropeng,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,200)}It's so cowardly. No...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.33,0:01:28.36,cloveropeng,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,200)}It's so difficult. I hate it. I hate it.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.07,0:01:38.76,clover,,0,0,0,,You've collected a lot.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.43,0:01:41.88,clover,,0,0,0,,A lot of them I got as souvenirs.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.42,0:01:46.28,clover,,0,0,0,,It's beautiful. The snow's all sparkly.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.28,0:01:48.14,clover,,0,0,0,,I love snow domes.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.17,0:01:52.52,clover,,0,0,0,,This one is a souvenir from Tatsukichi-san's honeymoon.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.96,0:01:54.34,clover,,0,0,0,,It's pretty!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.34,0:01:58.82,clover,,0,0,0,,It doesn't snow on the beaches of Hawaii, but it's kinda romantic.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.54,0:02:01.98,clover,,0,0,0,,Snow falling on sand dunes, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.03,0:02:08.37,clover,,0,0,0,,Snow falling on sand dunes, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.84,0:02:13.58,clover,,0,0,0,,Somehow, it's unbelievably surreal, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.58,0:02:17.17,clover,,0,0,0,,Well, the work that we're doing is absolutely surreal as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.70,0:02:20.53,clover,,0,0,0,,A German restaurant overlooking the sand dunes.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.53,0:02:23.37,clover,,0,0,0,,On top of that, it's next door to the Tottori Souvenir Center.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.37,0:02:25.64,clover,,0,0,0,,Luigi... Be a little more careful when choosing your work.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.07,0:02:30.56,clover,,0,0,0,,Actually, I'll bet this was a very romantic job from his point of view...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.56,0:02:33.23,clover,,0,0,0,,Luigi does love his junk...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.63,0:02:37.67,clover,,0,0,0,,Well, come December the snow really comes down here...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.67,0:02:38.98,clover,,0,0,0,,It's facing the Sea of Japan, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.08,0:02:42.52,clover,,0,0,0,,Snow falling on the sand dunes, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.52,0:02:44.44,clover,,0,0,0,,Well, it is picturesque.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.44,0:02:45.95,clover,,0,0,0,,It must be romantic...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.95,0:02:50.43,clover,,0,0,0,,If Miwako-san were by my side in that snow, I...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.76,0:02:52.64,clover,,0,0,0,,I... I...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.20,0:02:57.84,sign,,0,0,0,,{\fnMatura MT Script Capitals\c&H4A4A48&\3c&HFAF9FC&\an9\fs40\pos(658,7)\fad(500,0)}Yamazaki's Imagery
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.64,0:02:54.39,thoughts,,0,0,0,,Yamazaki, this is wonderful.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.39,0:02:57.84,thoughts,,0,0,0,,Thank you for showing me this beautiful scenery.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.88,0:03:03.17,sign,,0,0,0,,{\fnMatura MT Script Capitals\b1\3c&HFAF9FC&\an7\fs40\c&H515F79&\fad(200,0)}Nomiya's Imagery
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.12,0:03:01.51,thoughts,,0,0,0,,Sake is awesome!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.51,0:03:03.17,thoughts,,0,0,0,,Crab is awesome!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.95,0:03:07.59,clover,,0,0,0,,Don't you want to show Yamada-san the sand dunes?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.13,0:03:11.47,clover,,0,0,0,,Hm, I don't know...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.83,0:03:18.59,clover,,0,0,0,,You don't know?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.59,0:03:20.26,clover,,0,0,0,,Don't you want to see her?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.26,0:03:21.68,clover,,0,0,0,,Have you called her?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.68,0:03:22.40,clover,,0,0,0,,I haven't.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.40,0:03:24.96,clover,,0,0,0,,You haven't? You put it so bluntly...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.96,0:03:25.74,clover,,0,0,0,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.74,0:03:31.43,clover,,0,0,0,,Well, I'm not sure how to contact a girl who doesn't have a cell phone.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.43,0:03:34.63,clover,,0,0,0,,Oh, that's right, Yamada-san doesn't have a cell phone.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.63,0:03:36.37,clover,,0,0,0,,On top of that, she lives at home.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.27,0:03:40.12,clover,,0,0,0,,You saw her daddy, didn't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.12,0:03:43.73,clover,,0,0,0,,Yeah, I'd be afraid of that sentinel, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.00,0:03:46.97,note,,0,0,0,,[ Sign: Dedicated to Daughter ]
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.73,0:03:46.97,clover,,0,0,0,,I won't allow anyone near her!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.63,0:03:51.93,clover,,0,0,0,,Even so, don't you think about Yamada-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.46,0:03:55.43,clover,,0,0,0,,I do, but it's also a pain.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.49,0:03:57.60,clover,,0,0,0,,A pain?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.29,0:04:01.60,clover,,0,0,0,,I've never hurt a child before.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.13,0:04:05.90,clover,,0,0,0,,Just thinking about it makes me feel out of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.05,0:04:10.35,clover,,0,0,0,,Nomiya, Yamada-san is a full-fledged adult.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.35,0:04:12.08,clover,,0,0,0,,I'm talking about her mindset.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.48,0:04:16.17,clover,,0,0,0,,Yeah, I understand that, but... how do I say it...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.96,0:04:19.04,clover,,0,0,0,,What are you babbling about?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.59,0:04:21.31,clover,,0,0,0,,I don't get it.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.31,0:04:25.17,clover,,0,0,0,,Why do you assume that you'll hurt someone if you get involved with them?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.60,0:04:34.64,clover,,0,0,0,,I've always thought that once I find the right girl, I'll treasure her forever.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.23,0:04:36.70,clover,,0,0,0,,Isn't that how it's supposed to be?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.89,0:04:46.65,clover,,0,0,0,,Nomiya! Are you all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.65,0:04:47.90,clover,,0,0,0,,No, sand just got into my eyes...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.50,0:04:51.37,clover,,0,0,0,,Or more like... my eyes were just opened.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.19,0:04:55.20,clover,,0,0,0,,Yamada-san's been going to Rika-san's office?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.04,0:04:57.70,clover,,0,0,0,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.22,0:05:02.85,clover,,0,0,0,,Why would she go out of her way to stand under the waterfall?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.85,0:05:06.63,clover,,0,0,0,,It was something she needed to see for herself, even if it means getting beaten by a waterfall.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.00,0:05:06.63,dog,,0,0,0,,{\an1\move(707,373,88,373,0,3733)}Miwako-san... this sure is a wonderful night.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.14,0:05:08.72,clover,,0,0,0,,What an idiot.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.72,0:05:10.19,clover,,0,0,0,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.19,0:05:11.56,clover,,0,0,0,,She's an idiot.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.56,0:05:13.70,clover,,0,0,0,,So please give her a call.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.70,0:05:16.31,clover,,0,0,0,,She's at Harada Design on the weekends.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.91,0:05:21.70,thoughts,,0,0,0,,You're such a fool.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.37,0:05:26.85,thoughts,,0,0,0,,Was Mayama so important to you...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.19,0:05:29.97,thoughts,,0,0,0,,...that you need to jump into a meat shredder over it?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.82,0:05:40.31,clover,,0,0,0,,M-Mayama...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.46,0:05:43.25,clover,,0,0,0,,W-What are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.77,0:05:45.96,clover,,0,0,0,,Isn't that Rika-san's computer?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.28,0:05:50.01,clover,,0,0,0,,C-C-Could it be... that you've been browsing through her Internet history?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.32,0:05:53.97,clover,,0,0,0,,Well, um... I was just wondering if it's sunny in Hokkaido?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.97,0:05:57.34,clover,,0,0,0,,Mayama! Just how low will you go?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.34,0:05:58.96,clover,,0,0,0,,What about Hokkaido?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.96,0:05:59.85,clover,,0,0,0,,Oh, it's a fax!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.03,0:06:06.12,clover,,0,0,0,,Mayama...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.62,0:06:08.03,clover,,0,0,0,,What's the matter?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.02,0:06:10.78,clover,,0,0,0,,What's this request for an interview?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.78,0:06:14.25,clover,,0,0,0,,It says that you won the building expansion competition for the Valencia Museum of Art...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.25,0:06:16.78,clover,,0,0,0,,...and that you'll be working in Spain until it's finished.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.57,0:06:20.57,clover,,0,0,0,,It says that they would like to interview you beforehand...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.57,0:06:22.16,clover,,0,0,0,,Is this for real?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.58,0:06:26.03,clover,,0,0,0,,Yes, this is a job that I took with Harada-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.63,0:06:29.71,clover,,0,0,0,,It was on hold due to their circumstances, but now it's been restarted.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.17,0:06:32.14,clover,,0,0,0,,What are you going to do about this place?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.14,0:06:34.50,clover,,0,0,0,,You weren't going to discuss it with me?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.50,0:06:35.06,clover,,0,0,0,,I...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.06,0:06:36.43,clover,,0,0,0,,You're going as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.05,0:06:39.72,clover,,0,0,0,,Naturally, since it's work.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.20,0:06:45.06,clover,,0,0,0,,But that's still in the future.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.62,0:06:48.96,clover,,0,0,0,,For a while, we'll have a consultant work as an in-between...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.96,0:06:54.66,clover,,0,0,0,,...and we'll have to hammer out the paperwork for the contract for the next six months.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.12,0:07:00.72,clover,,0,0,0,,The interview request is too sudden, so I'll turn it down.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.60,0:07:03.80,clover,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.80,0:07:05.83,clover,,0,0,0,,I'm not feeling well.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.83,0:07:06.96,clover,,0,0,0,,I'm going back upstairs.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.73,0:07:13.67,clover,,0,0,0,,Hey, Yamada, what do you think this is?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.16,0:07:18.93,clover,,0,0,0,,A live camera for the weather forecast?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.93,0:07:20.56,clover,,0,0,0,,Otaru in Hokkaido.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.90,0:07:22.27,clover,,0,0,0,,It's her hometown.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.99,0:07:27.66,clover,,0,0,0,,She rarely speaks about herself.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.00,0:07:31.46,clover,,0,0,0,,But her Internet history is full of this site.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.31,0:07:39.62,clover,,0,0,0,,I noticed her staring at the monitor.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.62,0:07:43.16,clover,,0,0,0,,She hasn't taken a break in a long time.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.62,0:07:46.16,clover,,0,0,0,,She might still keep in touch with them...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.16,0:07:50.04,clover,,0,0,0,,...but she probably hasn't gone home in a long while.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.76,0:08:00.80,thoughts,,0,0,0,,You see, Rika, I want to make a container.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.21,0:08:03.95,thoughts,,0,0,0,,Not paintings or sculptures...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.38,0:08:07.78,thoughts,,0,0,0,,...but a huge house that can contain them all.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.58,0:08:09.84,thoughts,,0,0,0,,A huge house?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.14,0:08:11.07,thoughts,,0,0,0,,Like a museum?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.38,0:08:12.19,thoughts,,0,0,0,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.65,0:08:15.01,thoughts,,0,0,0,,Just like the one in Valencia that we saw on our senior trip.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.46,0:08:19.06,thoughts,,0,0,0,,A house that contains everything and stands serenely...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.06,0:08:22.12,thoughts,,0,0,0,,...atop a warm hill that smells of flowers all year round...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.93,0:08:24.12,clover,,0,0,0,,Harada-kun...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.67,0:08:27.12,clover,,0,0,0,,We made a lot of things together, didn't we?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.97,0:08:29.51,clover,,0,0,0,,It was so much fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.06,0:08:34.66,clover,,0,0,0,,But this is really the last one.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.22,0:08:39.77,clover,,0,0,0,,Harada-kun... Please wait for me...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.28,0:08:42.68,clover,,0,0,0,,I'm almost done.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.95,0:08:55.20,clover,,0,0,0,,Hello, this is Harada Design.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.20,0:08:56.65,clover,,0,0,0,,Oh, Nomiya-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.05,0:08:59.15,clover,,0,0,0,,Ah, so you're really there.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.15,0:09:00.83,clover,,0,0,0,,How did you know that I'd be here?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.14,0:09:03.04,clover,,0,0,0,,I heard from Miwako-san...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.04,0:09:05.12,clover,,0,0,0,,...that you're at Harada Design on the weekends.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.02,0:09:07.14,clover,,0,0,0,,It's been a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.14,0:09:08.15,clover,,0,0,0,,Have you been well?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.15,0:09:09.67,clover,,0,0,0,,Yes, of course!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.67,0:09:11.96,clover,,0,0,0,,How about you, Nomiya-san? Are you doing well?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.32,0:09:18.45,clover,,0,0,0,,I'm doing well, but it's seriously tough being together with Yamazaki day in and day out.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.45,0:09:20.68,clover,,0,0,0,,Together? Do you live in the same room with him?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.68,0:09:23.80,clover,,0,0,0,,Well, we have separate rooms, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.45,0:09:27.63,clover,,0,0,0,,...he comes every night to my room.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.63,0:09:30.39,clover,,0,0,0,,Saying "I'm bored" and stuff.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.51,0:09:30.39,clover,,0,0,0,,The hot pot is ready.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.77,0:09:32.80,clover,,0,0,0,,That's just like Yamazaki-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.80,0:09:37.11,clover,,0,0,0,,Either way, I was surprised to hear that you go there to help out.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.11,0:09:39.44,clover,,0,0,0,,Rika-san invited me.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.44,0:09:42.96,clover,,0,0,0,,She's actually let me make a lot of large potteries.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.96,0:09:45.81,clover,,0,0,0,,Rika-san has been treating me very well.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.81,0:09:48.53,clover,,0,0,0,,Oh, but Mayama is still the same.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.28,0:10:04.46,cloverinsert,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,200)}Woo Darlin' kanashii koto wa daiji na hito soko ni iru no ni\NWoo Darlin', the night will come and swallow your sorrow...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.53,0:09:53.17,clover,,0,0,0,,Tonight is out helping move an office he's familiar with.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.62,0:09:55.82,clover,,0,0,0,,Are you all right, Yamada-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.82,0:09:58.48,clover,,0,0,0,,Yeah! Things are going rather well.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.48,0:10:04.19,clover,,0,0,0,,Miwako-san and Rika-san have been taking such good care of me, so I'm really motivated to do well.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.46,0:10:07.86,clover,,0,0,0,,I'm also stockpiling some of my works...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.94,0:10:20.43,cloverinsert,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,200)}todokanu omoi no mama kyou mo yoru ga kite subete wo tsutsumu no\N...before it can reach the precious person right beside you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.86,0:10:09.82,clover,,0,0,0,,...since I want to make a portfolio.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.82,0:10:13.34,clover,,0,0,0,,Oh, and I've been thinking that it would be nice if I could make
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.34,0:10:16.73,clover,,0,0,0,,some sake sets to sell at home as gifts to complement the sake.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.73,0:10:22.74,clover,,0,0,0,,By the way, I'll be going to Miwako-san's tonight for Leader's birthday party!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.73,0:10:37.79,cloverinsert,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,200)}Woo Baby ai suru hito wa dakiau tabi namida wo nagasu\NWoo Baby, lovers will shed tears every time they embrace.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.74,0:10:24.16,clover,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.16,0:10:26.09,clover,,0,0,0,,Please give Miwako-san and Leader my regards.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.09,0:10:26.96,clover,,0,0,0,,Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.96,0:10:30.67,clover,,0,0,0,,Well, either way, I'm doing well over here...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.67,0:10:32.50,clover,,0,0,0,,...so please watch out for your health, Nomiya-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.93,0:10:34.52,clover,,0,0,0,,Don't push yourself too hard.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.52,0:10:36.55,clover,,0,0,0,,Yeah, I'll be fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.55,0:10:37.50,clover,,0,0,0,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.50,0:10:38.26,clover,,0,0,0,,Well then...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.26,0:10:41.67,clover,,0,0,0,,Okay, please give Yamazaki-san my regards then.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.30,0:10:53.84,cloverinsert,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,200)}furueru yubi wo tsutsundemo anata no kanashimi wo shiru ni wa tarinai\NHolding your shaking fingers won't be enough to know your sorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.28,0:10:43.45,clover,,0,0,0,,Gotcha.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.45,0:10:44.18,clover,,0,0,0,,See ya.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.49,0:10:45.73,clover,,0,0,0,,Have a good night.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.69,0:11:02.61,cloverinsert,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,200)}wakare no shunkan wa yami wo tsutatte\NThe moment we part will come through the dark...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.61,0:11:10.81,cloverinsert,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,200)}yagate omoide no subete wo itami ni kaeru\N...to turn all our memories into pain.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.81,0:11:18.96,cloverinsert,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,200)}kanjiru itami wa koko ni ita koto\NThe pain you feel is proof we were once here...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.91,0:11:18.18,clover,,0,0,0,,Welcome!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.96,0:11:27.64,cloverinsert,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,200)}furueru anata to koko ni ita koto\NProof that I was here with you in your sorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.77,0:11:22.17,clover,,0,0,0,,Please fill it up with premium. {note that premium gasoline does not make your car run faster}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.26,0:11:25.80,thoughts,,0,0,0,,Is she serious about "Don't push yourself too hard"?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.80,0:11:26.93,thoughts,,0,0,0,,Of course I'm going to!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.38,0:11:29.26,thoughts,,0,0,0,,Pretending to sound so happy like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.76,0:11:32.02,thoughts,,0,0,0,,I can't believe this...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.65,0:11:34.52,thoughts,,0,0,0,,It takes nine hours!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.47,0:11:45.61,clover,,0,0,0,,S-She headed off for Tottori...?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.61,0:11:50.37,dog,,0,0,0,,{\pos(358,371)\fs48}Wow, it's been a while!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.23,0:11:47.96,clover,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry, Nomiya!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.96,0:11:50.37,clover,,0,0,0,,Yamada-san seemed really depressed yesterday, so...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.37,0:11:52.58,dog,,0,0,0,,{\an7\fad(0,562)}Huh, why?\NI'm getting chills where\Nshe touched me?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.99,0:11:52.26,clover,,0,0,0,,Yamada-san...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.26,0:11:54.33,clover,,0,0,0,,Can you deliver this to Nomiya?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.37,0:11:55.37,dog,,0,0,0,,{\pos(235,368)\fs64}Ouch!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.02,0:11:57.46,clover,,0,0,0,,To... Nomiya-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.78,0:12:00.81,clover,,0,0,0,,That's right! Please go to Tottori for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.24,0:12:06.21,clover,,0,0,0,,To be honest, I was thinking, "Miwako, good job!" at the time.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.21,0:12:09.43,clover,,0,0,0,,I had no idea that you were headed this way...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.43,0:12:10.35,clover,,0,0,0,,Ouch...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.84,0:12:14.65,clover,,0,0,0,,But she's still on her way, so if we contact her...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.55,0:12:17.57,clover,,0,0,0,,She doesn't have a cellphone, does she?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.57,0:12:19.06,clover,,0,0,0,,This is the pits...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.65,0:12:20.99,clover,,0,0,0,,But Nomiya...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.99,0:12:23.30,clover,,0,0,0,,Why did you come to Tokyo all of a sudden?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.30,0:12:25.60,clover,,0,0,0,,You should have called.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.60,0:12:27.57,clover,,0,0,0,,Well, it was on a whim...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.57,0:12:30.37,clover,,0,0,0,,Since Yamada-san was saying that she'd be spending the night at your place.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.80,0:12:32.32,clover,,0,0,0,,Oh? That's it?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.69,0:12:34.62,clover,,0,0,0,,You came all the way from Tottori just for that?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.62,0:12:36.83,dog,,0,0,0,,{\pos(358,371)}Huff Huff Huff Huff Huff
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.24,0:12:40.21,clover,,0,0,0,,N-Nomiya... Could it be?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.21,0:12:41.80,clover,,0,0,0,,I'm heading back.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.80,0:12:43.13,clover,,0,0,0,,I'm gonna catch her no matter what.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.72,0:12:46.51,clover,,0,0,0,,Hey, why don't you get a little rest before you leave?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.11,0:12:49.03,clover,,0,0,0,,You drove here without sleeping, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.03,0:12:50.74,clover,,0,0,0,,What will you do if you get into an accident?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.74,0:12:53.47,clover,,0,0,0,,I'll take a nap on the rest area on the way.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.22,0:12:56.73,clover,,0,0,0,,Oh, and please contact Yamazaki.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.73,0:13:00.80,clover,,0,0,0,,Tell him, "Don't let her leave no matter what."
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.97,0:13:04.65,clover,,0,0,0,,Did you see that, Leader?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.13,0:13:10.52,clover,,0,0,0,,I can't believe he couldn't wait until morning to take a flight...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.52,0:13:12.74,clover,,0,0,0,,...and drove all the way from Tottori.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.53,0:13:18.79,clover,,0,0,0,,He's more manly now, compared to how smug he used to be.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.96,0:13:33.30,thoughts,,0,0,0,,You weren't going to discuss it with me?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.10,0:13:38.78,thoughts,,0,0,0,,She probably hasn't gone home in a long while.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.96,0:13:52.66,clover,,0,0,0,,Ah, Yamada-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.00,0:13:55.60,clover,,0,0,0,,Hey, over this way!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.59,0:13:59.31,clover,,0,0,0,,Oh, Yamazaki-san, it's been a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.31,0:14:00.82,clover,,0,0,0,,How have you been?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.82,0:14:04.17,clover,,0,0,0,,Y-Yamada-san, you're looking a little gaunt. Are you okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.95,0:14:07.60,clover,,0,0,0,,Nomiya-san isn't around?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.60,0:14:09.04,clover,,0,0,0,,T-That's...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.04,0:14:13.13,clover,,0,0,0,,He must be busy. It's unfortunate that I can't see him...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.13,0:14:14.42,clover,,0,0,0,,Well then...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.42,0:14:16.43,clover,,0,0,0,,Hey, wait a sec!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.75,0:14:19.44,clover,,0,0,0,,Since you came all the way out here, please take a tour of Tottori!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.43,0:14:21.44,sign,,0,0,0,,{\pos(260,280)\fnMatura MT Script Capitals\fs32\c&H000278&}Attended an All-Boys School\N(not good with girls)
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.44,0:14:21.74,clover,,0,0,0,,I'll take you around! I'll even pay.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.85,0:14:25.92,clover,,0,0,0,,Then let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.03,0:14:41.33,sign,,0,0,0,,{\fax-0.1\fnCambria\b1\3c&HCBD1DA&\c&H4E535E&\pos(103,34)\frz28.224}Breaking Point
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.67,0:14:40.86,clover,,0,0,0,,Thank you so much, Yamazaki-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.86,0:14:43.02,clover,,0,0,0,,Today was a lot of fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.02,0:14:43.87,clover,,0,0,0,,Y-Yeah?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.49,0:14:48.05,clover,,0,0,0,,It went by in a flash, but I'm starting to feel better.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.05,0:14:49.00,clover,,0,0,0,,Yeah?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.00,0:14:51.51,clover,,0,0,0,,But I need to get going soon...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.51,0:14:56.47,sign,,0,0,0,,{\fs36\fax-0.1\fnCambria\b1\3c&HCBD1DA&\c&H4E535E&\pos(103,34)\frz28.224}Breaking Point!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.51,0:14:53.19,clover,,0,0,0,,Now, now, now!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.19,0:14:55.62,clover,,0,0,0,,Nomiya will be back soon, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.62,0:14:56.15,clover,,0,0,0,,Okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.15,0:14:56.47,clover,,0,0,0,,Okay?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.47,0:14:59.08,clover,,0,0,0,,N-Nomiya!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.51,0:15:00.73,clover,,0,0,0,,Thank goodness...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.73,0:15:02.24,clover,,0,0,0,,It's been a while!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.24,0:15:05.10,clover,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry for intruding when you're so busy...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.99,0:15:09.27,clover,,0,0,0,,I'm glad that I got to see you, since I need to go soon...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.65,0:15:11.03,clover,,0,0,0,,Please don't leave.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.67,0:15:19.82,clover,,0,0,0,,I'll talk to you when I wake up, so please stay here.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.24,0:15:23.41,clover,,0,0,0,,U-Um, Nomiya-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.79,0:15:24.74,clover,,0,0,0,,All right!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.48,0:15:32.41,clover,,0,0,0,,4946 for Nomiya!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.48,0:15:32.41,note,,0,0,0,,Note: "Shi-Ku-Yo-Ro" (4946), when rearranged, becomes "yoroshiku" meaning "please take care of him".
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.30,0:15:37.13,clover,,0,0,0,,T-That's...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.13,0:15:38.72,clover,,0,0,0,,What's 4946?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.95,0:16:06.41,clover,,0,0,0,,W-Whoa...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.84,0:16:08.39,thoughts,,0,0,0,,The hell you want?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.39,0:16:10.00,thoughts,,0,0,0,,What you think you're staring at, dammit!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.46,0:16:12.38,sign,,0,0,0,,{\fad(1000,0)\pos(358,365)\fnCalibri\c&H000000&\3c&HE2E7E7&}An Entourage of Holy Beasts (Unicorns) Defending the Maiden's Chastity
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.00,0:16:11.55,thoughts,,0,0,0,,Wanna go, ya bastard?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.55,0:16:13.18,thoughts,,0,0,0,,Wanna get pummeled, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.00,0:16:16.84,sign,,0,0,0,,{\fad(319,0)\pos(213,324)\fnConstantia\b1\c&H000000&\3c&HFFFFFF&}Hiding her head
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.18,0:16:16.84,clover,,0,0,0,,I wonder what kind of torture this is?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.05,0:16:16.84,sign,,0,0,0,,{\fad(354,0)\fnConstantia\b1\3c&HFFFFFF&\1c&H000000&\pos(516,324)}But not her legs
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.70,0:16:23.15,clover,,0,0,0,,Ah, geez. Yeah, yeah, out of my way already.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.15,0:16:24.44,thoughts,,0,0,0,,That hurt, dammit!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.44,0:16:26.05,thoughts,,0,0,0,,I'm gonna impale you, dammit!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.63,0:16:29.32,clover,,0,0,0,,Rest well, sweet honey.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.97,0:16:35.18,clover,,0,0,0,,Yamada-san, please wake up.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.18,0:16:36.24,clover,,0,0,0,,It's morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.99,0:16:40.45,sign,,0,0,0,,{\fnComic Sans MS\b1\bord1.5\pos(358,330)\fs36\c&H6675CE&\3c&H41494D&}Offerings
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.99,0:16:39.44,clover,,0,0,0,,Delish, dammit!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.44,0:16:40.45,clover,,0,0,0,,This is delish, dammit!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.95,0:16:45.20,clover,,0,0,0,,Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.16,0:16:47.41,clover,,0,0,0,,Nomiya-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.22,0:16:52.09,clover,,0,0,0,,This is the third time I've seen you wake up.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.38,0:16:54.89,clover,,0,0,0,,Oh, you have bread...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.74,0:16:57.29,clover,,0,0,0,,Here you go.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.29,0:16:59.21,clover,,0,0,0,,Thanks for the meal...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.27,0:17:05.49,clover,,0,0,0,,Oh, it's good...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.49,0:17:08.22,clover,,0,0,0,,Once you finish eating those, let's go see the sand dunes.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.22,0:17:10.51,clover,,0,0,0,,Sand dunes?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.51,0:17:12.44,clover,,0,0,0,,You have some time until your train leaves, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.16,0:17:15.03,clover,,0,0,0,,Wow!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.65,0:17:17.96,clover,,0,0,0,,They're huge when you see them up close!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.96,0:17:20.74,clover,,0,0,0,,It's amazing that there's a place like this in Japan.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.12,0:17:23.70,clover,,0,0,0,,You should take off your shoes.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.70,0:17:27.87,clover,,0,0,0,,Once you get sand in them, you can't get it out, since the grains are too fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.90,0:17:34.95,clover,,0,0,0,,Oh, that's right. Where were you yesterday, Nomiya-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.95,0:17:37.50,clover,,0,0,0,,Oh, I was in Tokyo.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.50,0:17:39.08,clover,,0,0,0,,Huh, Tokyo?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.08,0:17:40.53,clover,,0,0,0,,Was it for work?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.27,0:17:48.03,clover,,0,0,0,,I went to see you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.74,0:18:00.19,clover,,0,0,0,,So what's the real reason?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.81,0:18:03.11,clover,,0,0,0,,Did something happen?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.03,0:18:07.85,clover,,0,0,0,,You were sobbing when I called you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.85,0:18:09.20,clover,,0,0,0,,I-I wasn't!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.56,0:18:12.47,clover,,0,0,0,,Really? Then it must've been after I got off the phone with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.41,0:18:17.64,clover,,0,0,0,,H-H-H-H-How? Nomiya-san, how did you...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.97,0:18:20.66,clover,,0,0,0,,Oh, I wonder why...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.08,0:18:26.27,thoughts,,0,0,0,,I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.08,0:18:30.27,thoughts,,0,0,0,,I mean, I've be watching you all this time.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.72,0:18:35.61,thoughts,,0,0,0,,You just didn't notice because you were always looking at Mayama.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.58,0:18:39.67,thoughts,,0,0,0,,Yamada-san...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.19,0:18:44.78,thoughts,,0,0,0,,The guy that you're in love with is going to go far away with another woman.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.75,0:18:48.49,thoughts,,0,0,0,,Even so, I'm not going to say anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.36,0:18:52.62,thoughts,,0,0,0,,I bet you still have a lot of crying to do...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.63,0:18:59.25,thoughts,,0,0,0,,Once you're crushed, I'll show up with an understanding expression and listen to what you have to say.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.05,0:19:02.97,thoughts,,0,0,0,,You must've cried your heart out already...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.85,0:19:07.22,thoughts,,0,0,0,,I just want to speak kind words to you and caution you a little.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.09,0:19:12.08,thoughts,,0,0,0,,But you still need to cry even more...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.45,0:19:16.73,thoughts,,0,0,0,,And you'll come to be by my side.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.77,0:19:23.75,thoughts,,0,0,0,,But you'll probably choose to cry...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.36,0:19:31.37,thoughts,,0,0,0,,Somewhere far away, where I can't console you...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.97,0:19:33.06,thoughts,,0,0,0,,All alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.46,0:19:38.88,clover,,0,0,0,,It was a lot of fun!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.52,0:19:44.31,clover,,0,0,0,,And you bought me so many souvenirs...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.63,0:19:45.97,clover,,0,0,0,,Thank you so much.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.71,0:19:48.64,clover,,0,0,0,,I'm glad that I saw the sand dunes.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.64,0:19:49.75,clover,,0,0,0,,They were beautiful.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.34,0:19:53.35,clover,,0,0,0,,I'm starting to feel better, so I'll do my best!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.15,0:19:58.27,clover,,0,0,0,,Nomiya-san, please watch out for your health and do your best at work.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.58,0:20:01.02,clover,,0,0,0,,Um, well then.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.18,0:20:03.15,clover,,0,0,0,,Yamada-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.76,0:20:10.53,clover,,0,0,0,,When you feel helpless, please call me.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.05,0:20:14.61,clover,,0,0,0,,S-Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.61,0:20:16.94,clover,,0,0,0,,But why are you saying that?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.12,0:20:23.53,clover,,0,0,0,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.25,0:20:27.05,clover,,0,0,0,,It's because I'm in love with you!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.05,0:20:29.02,clover,,0,0,0,,{\an8}The train on platform 4 is departing.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.02,0:20:31.03,clover,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Please be careful of the closing doors.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.41,0:20:50.69,clover,,0,0,0,,What am I being all honest for?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.82,0:20:56.99,clover,,0,0,0,,Nomiya...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.88,0:21:00.44,clover,,0,0,0,,This is the pits...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.13,0:21:05.76,sign,,0,0,0,,{\c&H000000&\fnCalibri\pos(467,5)\3c&HEFEFEF&}Please wait a moment {\c&H6160DD&}(processing capacity exceeded)
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.76,0:21:09.13,clover,,0,0,0,,Nomiya, I'm incredibly moved right now!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.97,0:21:10.97,sign,,0,0,0,,{\fnFutura LT Heavy\bord2\an9\c&HAAADF4&\3c&HE7EFEC&}Nomiya Takumi - re-equipped with the suit of adolescence!!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.13,0:21:10.97,clover,,0,0,0,,We're going to drink the night away!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.00,0:21:14.15,thoughts,,0,0,0,,All hands, return to Kanto, dammit!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.15,0:21:15.63,thoughts,,0,0,0,,Don't lose sight of her, dammit!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.63,0:21:16.27,thoughts,,0,0,0,,Return at once, dammit!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.27,0:21:17.33,thoughts,,0,0,0,,We're calling for backup, dammit!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.33,0:21:19.01,thoughts,,0,0,0,,The princess is in a pinch, dammit!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.60,0:21:29.74,cloveredrom,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,300)}arifurete iru kimochi nante sa
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.60,0:21:29.74,cloveredeng,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,300)}It would be so much easier...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.10,0:21:40.20,cloveredrom,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,0)}nanimo iwazu ni isso kieteshimaeba
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.10,0:21:40.20,cloveredeng,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,0)}...if these stale emotions...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.20,0:21:43.62,cloveredrom,,0,0,0,,raku ni nareru no ni
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.20,0:21:43.62,cloveredeng,,0,0,0,,...could just disappear without a word.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.62,0:21:52.75,cloveredrom,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,300)}sorezore no michi wo yuku sono wakaremichi
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.62,0:21:52.75,cloveredeng,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,300)}At the crossroads where we split ways...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.30,0:22:06.23,cloveredrom,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,0)}mou nidoto au koto no nai deai wa kanashisugiru
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.30,0:22:06.23,cloveredeng,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,0)}...it saddens me to think we may never meet again.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.23,0:22:08.97,cloveredrom,,0,0,0,,tarinai kimochi wo mochiyotte
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.23,0:22:08.97,cloveredeng,,0,0,0,,Despite adding the emotions that are lacking...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.97,0:22:11.83,cloveredrom,,0,0,0,,atatameta saki kara hieteitte
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.97,0:22:11.83,cloveredeng,,0,0,0,,...things cool off just as soon as I warm them...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.83,0:22:16.17,cloveredrom,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,300)}sonna hazu naitte shinjiteru
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.83,0:22:16.17,cloveredeng,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,300)}...but I still don't want to believe.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.54,0:22:24.87,cloveredrom,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,0)}ittai itsumade onaji kotoba wo kakaekondenda
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.54,0:22:24.87,cloveredeng,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,0)}Just how long am I going to brood over the same word?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.87,0:22:28.27,cloveredrom,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,300)}kakekondenda
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.87,0:22:28.27,cloveredeng,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,300)}How long...?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.69,0:22:34.27,clover,,0,0,0,,Next episode: I won't let you go anywhere.
